{"tid":1899140,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「多圖預警」多一萬又唔會發達，少咗又唔會窮⋯","createTime":"2020-02-26T11:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T12:13:19.000Z","uid":114360,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"229d90080e57ed6544ba32d03d33d0905e4ffe1f","tid":1899140,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"「多一萬又唔會發達，少咗又唔會窮⋯」<br />\n<br />\n有時，我怕自己睇嘢有盲點，盲撐某種聲音。於是，我會問年逾半百媽媽意見。<br />\n<br />\n我向她解釋，若要袋一萬元，便要通過警察加薪，畀警察買多6架裝甲車，用6億買催淚彈，請多2500人......<br />\n<br />\n「你認真答我，你仲要唔要呢一萬？」<br />\n<br />\n「咁呀⋯同班差人一齊攬炒⋯老實講，多一萬蚊又唔會發達，少咗又唔會窮⋯我唔要呢一萬蚊！」<br />\n<br />\n媽媽繼續說下去。<br />\n<br />\n「見到班差人咁樣打人，睇電視我都會喊，唔可能贊成佢哋拎多啲糧，打更多人！」<br />\n<br />\n也許錢再多，也買不下良知。一棍棍底下，沾滿了鮮血，血跡抹得走，疤痕擦不去。<br />\n<br />\n各位非建制議員，社會意見很清晰，用盡一切方法，也要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">阻止通過財委會警察加薪方案</span></strong>，阻止財政預算案表決。<br />\n<br />\n一萬背後，後患無窮。<br />\n<br />\n**一生一世，也忘不了理大那場仗。<br />\n<br />\nsource：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108970510452155/posts/197446368271235/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108970510452155%2Fposts%2F197446368271235%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=158728a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108970510452155/posts/197446368271235/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spANiFP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FspANiFP.png&h=fe7d395b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pFu6zea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpFu6zea.png&h=48cc47d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qkm45kR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQkm45kR.png&h=12bc0416&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mVTyYFT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmVTyYFT.png&h=399c8c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QRmD9Nz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQRmD9Nz.png&h=94bbefa3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MOGs27A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMOGs27A.png&h=a4c72812&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDx727B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDx727B.png&h=2a3cbabf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RL0YqkX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRL0YqkX.png&h=9fd557af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ooAUH7D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FooAUH7D.png&h=132c24d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516f430a7460d615f421a470d32fb098306a45af","tid":1899140,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係我地對你地唔住"},{"pid":"c44320762a44fc9898c9e4a678745d13d3d72d89","tid":1899140,"uid":33874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"係，但你唔攞撚咗佢<br />\n警察加完薪會用埋你嗰一萬買gear買車出糧<br />\n而你一蚊都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊錢就介咗出嚟，點都會用撚咗佢"},{"pid":"ff39fa48d0a9d44c8b1e18294f4496bfb9e9d540","tid":1899140,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c44320762a44fc9898c9e4a678745d13d3d72d89","tid":1899140,"uid":33874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"係，但你唔攞撚咗佢<br />\n警察加完薪會用埋你嗰一萬買gear買車出糧<br />\n而你一蚊都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊錢就介咗出嚟，點都會用撚咗佢"},"citedBy":